  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 33\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Over 33 million Keralas smoke cannabis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that 113 kilos and 280 grams of Kerala cannabis, worth over 33 million rupees, were found yesterday (10th) while they were piled up in the Urumalai seashore area of \u200b\u200bWelipara area of \u200b\u200bMannar.",
        "When a group of officers of the North Central Naval Command conducted a search patrol in Mannar Welipara Urumalai beach area, first 105 kg of Kerala ganja belonging to 24 bags and then another 8 kg of 280 grams were found piled up on the beach.",
        "The navy also suspects that the Kerala ganja stock may have been brought to Mannar by sea from India and the smugglers saw the navy and fled to the sea.",
        "The navy also said that steps have been taken to hand over the seized stock of Kerala ganja to the police for further investigation."
      ],
